title: 3BR / Near Baker Beach, Remodeled / Clement @ 24th Ave
posting_body: ['3BR / Near Baker Beach, Remodeled / Clement @ 24th', 'Ave', 'This is a street-level flat in a Victorian building located on the corner of 24th and Clement.', 'This flat has been completely remodeled with new Brazilian Cherry kitchen cabinets and appliances.', 'The flat is very cozy with cool recessed lighting and birch-toned tile floors.', 'The flat features a newly remodeled kitchen with 3 independent rooms and 1 bathroom.', 'There is a wash/dryer inside the building.', 'This neighborhood is excellent.', ' Perfect for students.', ' There are numerous restaurants in the area and still only a few blocks to the secluded Baker Beach.', ' Also only one block away from major MUNI stops.', 'Close to GG Bridge, Highway 101, GG Park, China Beach, and Ocean Beach.', ' Very accessible to USF, UCSF, San Francisco Art Institute, San Francisco Culinary Academy, San Francisco Cooking School, and SF State.', 'Call Irene for more info or to see the flat.', ' Irene can be reached at', 'show contact info', '.', 'Only available for Non-Smokers.', '  Sorry, no pets.', '---------------------------']
